      "side": 1,
      "message": "Line 1487: 🟡 Suggestion: When re-cloning, `removed` and `erased` are reset but `members` is not refreshed. If the member set changed while the user was absent (members added or removed), the local `conv-\u003einfo.members` may be stale until the clone completes and syncs. Consider adding a log or comment noting that the member set will be reconciled during the clone/sync phase, to make the intent clear to future readers.",
