      "side": 1,
      "message": "Line 2005: 🟡 Suggestion: The re-invite path does not validate that the incoming request\u0027s mode matches the mode of the existing removed conversation. A malformed or malicious request could claim a different mode than what the original conversation was. Although `cloneConversationFrom` performs its own ONE_TO_ONE check, consider adding a consistency check here:\n```suggestion\n        if (!pimpl_-\u003eisRemovedGroupConversation(convId)\n            || req.mode() \u003d\u003d ConversationMode::ONE_TO_ONE) {\n            return;\n        }\n```\nThis makes the `onConversationRequest` gate consistent with the `cloneConversationFrom` gate and rejects bad requests earlier.",
